@just an Espeon even regular command spells are gonna vary a ton. Stronger servants can resist them, especially most Archers with Independent Action. It's also going to depend heavily in the Master's own mana. Finally, it.will work far better if it's a simpler, short, direct command. "Become my sex slave" won't work, at best you'll manage a "take off your shirt" - something they can do immediately and the command lasts for a short while.

Fate Stay Night starts off with Rin giving Archer a far vague "obey me" type of command with one of her seals, and Archer even explains these issues to her, but she still manages to have him feel the pull toward listening to her. This is because she's that talented of a magus though.
